486
00:15:59,426 --> 00:16:01,058
           Scratch-made.        
   We don't have a freezer here,

487
00:16:01,127 --> 00:16:03,027
          so everything's fresh.
Really?                         

488
00:16:03,029 --> 00:16:04,294
    Here's your flamethrower    
        and French fries.       

489
00:16:04,331 --> 00:16:07,165
 MAN: The flamethrower is meaty.
            It's hot.           

490
00:16:07,167 --> 00:16:08,499
        One of the Bart's       
        great sandwiches.       

491
00:16:08,501 --> 00:16:09,633
   So, what are we              
   going to make?               

492
00:16:09,669 --> 00:16:12,836
          Habanero salsa for our
            flamethrower panini.

493
00:16:12,872 --> 00:16:15,239
We're going to make a panini    
that has habanero salsa in it?  

494
00:16:15,375 --> 00:16:16,975
                  Yes.          
         I think you'll like it.

495
00:16:17,110 --> 00:16:18,842
   Okay.                        
        Got some habaneros here.

496
00:16:18,878 --> 00:16:22,380
  Put in a little bit of carrot,
   white onion, pineapple juice.

497
00:16:22,449 --> 00:16:24,382
       Blend it up a little bit.

498
00:16:24,384 --> 00:16:28,186
             Lemon juice, cumin,
