499
00:16:28,321 --> 00:16:30,054
That's not going to be hot.     

500
00:16:30,189 --> 00:16:32,256
       Leave some texture to it.

501
00:16:32,258 --> 00:16:33,524
  Let it simmer for             
  about 10 minutes,             

502
00:16:33,560 --> 00:16:35,460
and that's the beginning        
of this flamethrower.           

503
00:16:35,462 --> 00:16:36,593
                    Yes.        

504
00:16:36,629 --> 00:16:38,596
 I just want to know            
why you call it that.           

505
