00:16:49,609 --> 00:16:51,942
         We put it in the smoker
            about 190 to 200.   

513
00:16:51,978 --> 00:16:54,011
    And when it gets to the nice
         sweet spot for pulling,

514
00:16:54,014 --> 00:16:58,149
   I'll let it rest a little bit
         and then pull it apart.

515
00:16:58,151 --> 00:16:59,484
  Yep, that'll do.              

516
00:16:59,486 --> 00:17:02,553
            Take our roast beef,
      a little bit of pork here.

517
00:17:02,555 --> 00:17:04,021
    Got to get some             
