523
00:17:14,267 --> 00:17:16,700
 Pickled jalapeños.             

524
00:17:16,770 --> 00:17:17,969
  Fresh jalapeños.              

525
00:17:18,104 --> 00:17:19,503
Yeah, that's not going          
to be hot or anything.          

526
00:17:19,572 --> 00:17:23,173
Hey, why don't we hit it with   
