00:17:56,409 --> 00:17:58,676
      -Excellent, brother.      
    -Flamethrower, fries up.    

543
00:17:58,811 --> 00:17:59,810
      One of my favorites.      

544
00:17:59,813 --> 00:18:01,679
        -It packs a heat.       
         -Yes, it does!         

